        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='12857' id='18' type-v2='text' w='45474' x='2474' y='76333'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='18'>UK Revenue:</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='18'>The United Kingdom dominates market share, generating 91.8% ($637.5K) of total revenue. Core expansion markets Germany ($11.9K, 1.7%), France ($7.7K, 1.1%), and Australia ($965, 0.1%)  represent just 3% combined, highlighting a significant geographic concentration risk and an optimal target for localized regional ad spending to diversify revenue.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone h='30619' id='19' name='Sheet 8' w='45053' x='3579' y='42667' />
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='12190' id='20' type-v2='text' w='47684' x='50211' y='77000'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='18'>Repeat Buyers:</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='18'>Only 27.8% of customers are repeat buyers, yet they generate 43.3% of total revenue  meaning loyal customers are worth significantly more per head than one-time buyers. Investing in a retention strategy such as loyalty discounts or re-engagement emails could meaningfully grow revenue without acquiring new customers.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='8476' id='21' type-v2='text' w='52474' x='21000' y='90619'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='15'>Top Product:</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='15'>REGENCY CAKESTAND 3 TIER is the top revenue-generating retail product at $23,556 (3.4% of total revenue) — more than double the next best seller, WHITE HANGING HEART T-LIGHT HOLDER ($10,373). Note: DOTCOM POSTAGE ($17,095) and AMAZON FEE ($13,541) appear in the top 5 but are fulfilment costs, not sellable products, and should be excluded from product performance reporting.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
